				I finally got the earring! I logged on at around 9 in the morning, he spawned at 2:35pm, I killed him, no earring. Add 5 (hours) to 2:35pm and you'll figure out that he was going to spawn at 7:00 even, BUT since it can be from 5 to 6+ hours, I added 1 hour just in case, so it turned out to be 8:00 (give or take 15mins). I stayed on camping him the whole day, practicing Conjuration and Tracking. Finally he spawned at 8:05. Killed him, got the earring. VERY boring wait, but WELL worth it!<BR>
