				Ok update on the times here people READ THIS!<BR>
<BR>
After Hadden is killed he has a spawn time of, read this carefully, 5 hours 18 mins he WILL NOT spawn before this time, and he can spawn at anytime up to 40 mins after the 5 hours 18 mins. There was 4 of us that camped Hadden (shifts) over a 4 day period, and in this time only 4 earrings dropped. All of the spawn times were written down each time he popped....the majority of the time he spawned right at 5 hours 18 mins, 2 times he went all the way to the 40 min time mark.<BR>
<BR>
So if you get there and sit for 3 hours and he spawns does not mean he has a 3 hour spawn time.
